                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Bhawna Foundation was established in 2015 with a vision to create a world where every individual, regardless of their background, has access to quality education, healthcare, and opportunities for growth.",
